OL,4,CEvery customer must sign in when pubs
OL,5,Creopen
OL,6, New rules to help pubs, cafes and
OL,7, restaurants reopen outdoors safely in
OL,8, England on 12 April have sparked anger
OL,9, from industry groups.
OL,11,FAll customers will have to sign in on
OL,12,Fentry, not just one member of the group
OL,13,Flike before. It is also unclear whether
OL,14,Fpayment at the bar will be permitted.
OL,16,FUK Hospitality said it would burden
OL,17,Fstruggling pubs and staff and risk
OL,18,Fcustomers deciding not to go out.
OL,20,FThe BBC has contacted the Cabinet
OL,21,FOffice for a comment.
